{"tid":2330573,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"結婚四年 | Rain自爆主動追金泰希：暗戀了她一年","createTime":"2020-12-18T06:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T14:38:50.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e79038bba788e6a1f4264334752323afc88bda","tid":2330573,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YHp2r2GLOa8DkLNaq2HN_ZrxT50=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VSALIUS2BZCARFPADS6OSQJVIU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYHp2r2GLOa8DkLNaq2HN_ZrxT50%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVSALIUS2BZCARFPADS6OSQJVIU.jpg&h=e8143594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現年38歲的韓流天王Rain和40歲的金泰希下月結婚四周年，兩人育有兩女，組織一家四口幸福家庭。Rain於2013年被爆與金泰希拍拖，拍拖多年後於大前年1月結婚，成為圈中的模範夫妻。<br />\n<br />\n到fans家炮製美食<br />\nRain事隔三年回歸樂壇，近日密密keep住曝光率keep住人氣，他又在YouTube開設個人頻道「Season B Season」，並邀請不同嘉賓上節目。而於昨日公開的片段中，Rain就到訪某位fans的屋企，並親自下廚為fans炮製美食。<br />\n<br />\n片段中，fans問到偶像如何與金泰希開始發展，Rain就大方說：「是我主動的，花了很長時間呢，暗戀了她一年，（能與她結婚）現在也像做夢一樣。」展現其純情男以及對妻子愛意的一面。<br />\n<br />\n張聖圭愛妻係fans<br />\n之後，Rain又到訪問了其他fans的家中，而這位fans原來是著名主持人張聖圭的妻子，令觀眾大感驚喜。張聖圭的妻子見到偶像即變成「少女fans」，掩飾不住內心的激動，十分搞笑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201218/OTB4GETYUNFLZC3I6AVWHU6Z4A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201218%2FOTB4GETYUNFLZC3I6AVWHU6Z4A%2F&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrTk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=6206672a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201218%2FOTB4GETYUNFLZC3I6AVWHU6Z4A%2F&h=e5d6ecb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201218/OTB4GETYUNFLZC3I6AVWHU6Z4A/</a>"},{"pid":"7e54682e969c7e018007ede682e53832c2192a6a","tid":2330573,"uid":261849,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:29:40.000Z","msg":"真係後生過老婆個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944e95df10096d310f205d6e2a0b29b926d1a2b0","tid":2330573,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:31:07.000Z","msg":"羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7885da09a758773c07a2a49f4bb1b216da6ac06e","tid":2330573,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7e54682e969c7e018007ede682e53832c2192a6a","tid":2330573,"uid":261849,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:29:40.000Z","msg":"真係後生過老婆個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:31:22.000Z","msg":"返老還童<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ca0af16dfd5a175d4f58208fe13ac048dea844","tid":2330573,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:36:44.000Z","msg":"啲肌肉消左大半咁"},{"pid":"9d940b558af1ce8fc6179222a262059afcc62f02","tid":2330573,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7e54682e969c7e018007ede682e53832c2192a6a","tid":2330573,"uid":261849,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:29:40.000Z","msg":"真係後生過老婆個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:49:54.000Z","msg":"本身靚底，人生贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542de90fb2a12c6ef9483cb89281eb4efaf52675","tid":2330573,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T08:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e23